description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to welcome a Deputy Head of Technology and Cyber Security Manager at Northampton General Hospital. This role will take responsibility for supporting the Head of Technology in the day to day running of the Trust&#39;s Technology team and managing the Trust&#39;s cyber security team to maintain security and protection for the Trust. The successful applicant will be an expert source of advice and expertise in Information Technology and Cyber Security, as well as ensuring that systems and processes are in place to ensure compliance with all statutory and regulatory requirements relating to Cyber Security and the Data Security and Protection Toolkit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is an opportunity for someone with the appropriate skills, experience and qualifications. The role will suit someone who has worked in a similar role in a health or social care setting, is highly motivated and is looking for a new challenge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role requires the post holder to advise on technology and cyber security issues whilst maintaining objectivity and maintaining the highest professional standards and ethics. You will provide independent scrutiny on issues relating to cyber security whilst working in close relationship with relevant stakeholders including external partners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will have experience delivering change with strong leadership skills as well as practical experience within an Information Technology/Cyber Security environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to support the Trust and work in a fast paced IT &lt;/span&gt;environment&lt;span&gt; where you are able &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;to make a difference. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Dave Smith, Job title: Head of Technology, Email address: dave.smith@ngh.nhs.uk, Telephone number: 01604 523595, Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Lewis Chinnick at Lewis.Chinnick@ngh.nhs.uk &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
